FAQ

Questions that often arise regarding Graphic Design Services
Will we only accept 1 design?

If you need several design options to choose from, you can convey them to us. We will provide design by request options

Will I get the raw files?

Of course. We will provide soft files and print files so that if in the future there is something you want to change, you can change it as you wish.

What if in the future there is still something that needs to be revised?

You can contact us again for further communication.
